a complete analysis of my fugly testimonail


Interpersonal Qualities

xx is an extremely entertaining friend.

sounds not bad

xx is known for her funny re-enactments, and does not mind sharing embarrassing moments.

tell me what is this! am i a clown?!

Her willingness to make jokes at her own expense reflects her self-assurance and generosity.

making jokes at my own expense reflects my self-assurance and generosity?! self assurance comes from confidence and generosisty is more like helping others?!

Peers find her approachable, and she readily extends her help and company, even for tasks that are not to her preference.

finally a nice sentence

xx makes great company, whether as homework bearer or gym buddy.

i'm sure they care i make a good homework bearer or gym buddy

xx's positive approach to life inspires much joy.

this sounds classy

Her warmth was particularly appreciated by a classmate, who felt accepted after initial feelings of alienation.

eh who?!

xx's humour is a great source of encouragement for her classmates during difficult times.

thats good

For instance, along the course of Project Work, her group members appreciated her company when completing less savoury tasks. As one classmate aptly puts it, "xx has a silly face and a silly smile. She does not realise it, but she brightens up people's lives".

ok. this sounds good too but seriously i feel like i'm described as someone who is mental and keep smiling or laughing for no reason. ohwells

As a group member, xx respects the thinking and viewpoints of others.

yes. good

She is sensitive to their emotions, and always ready to accommodate other people's points of interests.

yupyup. good sc

She commits herself to the group's direction, following the team leader's instructions and encouraging fellow members.

GOOD

She enjoys the trust of peers, who entrust her with responsibilities such as the safekeeping of money and valuables for the group.

WONDERFUL. although i don't rmb that happening


Intrapersonal Qualities

Through her involvement in Judo, xx showed much character.

impressive start

New to the sport, she was highly motivated, improved steadily within a few months, and represented the College in the Nationals single and team events.

yes yes. good point noted

After suffering an injury to the anterior cruciate ligament (ACL), she underwent ACL reconstruction, and persevered through the post-surgery physiotherapy sessions.

YEAH! IMAGINE THE PAIN!

This was an extremely difficult time for her, not only because physiotherapy constantly challenged her physical limits.

yes yes. leg press still gives me nightmares

She also had to prepare for the Promotional examinations at the same time.

which she got the shittiest results ever

Despite the mental toll, she pulled herself through.

be proud of me!

xx's resolute determination extends to her beliefs and principles.

nice sentence

She upholds them with conviction, remaining steadfast to the point of stubbornness.

i have no idea why i tink i sound like a donkey

Her mental strength is reflected in her metaphor of examinations as a battlefield, in which she likes to imagine herself as the victor.

i think by the point people read to this sentence
they would be extremely convinced that i'm mental

xx is a battler, not a passive sufferer.

ok true. but. DOESNT SOUND NICE LAR!


Intellectual Qualities

xx has a lively mind that is receptive to new ideas. With friends, she discusses controversial issues with an open mind. During Project Work, she often came up with alternatives in quick response to current circumstances.


you know. looking at how short it is. it plainly reflects how pea-ed my brain is. people won't even bother to read and they get the idea that. "ohwow. this girl is a bimbo. OUT"


in conclusion
i'm going to have a difficult time presenting myself to the university next time
that is if i ever make it
i will never move on if i dwell in the past
